letter, 12pt single spaced). The material must be original and previously
unpublished. Parallel submissions to other conferences is possible but must be
indicated with the submission. The material that is covered in the abstract must
be appropriate in length and content to be presented in a 30-minute talk.
Submissions must be made before 30 May and sent to one of the following
addresses: Alain.Lecomte@univ-paris8.fr,
quatrini@iml.univ-mrs.fr

